						<a class="title" href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,3126438)"></a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tl333s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1304786); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1304786&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610227299" alt="TL333s" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1304786)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tl333s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1304786); return false;" >TL333s</a></span>, <span class="odate time_1499427568 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">07 Jul 2017 11:39</span>
